{"tid":1187019,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅智光：公務員有需要了解內地社會發展和政治體制等","createTime":"2019-06-05T10:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T11:49:00.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9936d286297faa452d8ee9f23791b260a1be8b8f","tid":1187019,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190605_20190605-175908.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190605_20190605-175908.jpg&h=81aea552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會辯論改善公務員待遇的無約束力議案，公務員事務局長羅智光表示，感謝公務員不辭勞苦，全心全意工作，政府已適當增加人手，加強培訓，提供合適的薪酬待遇。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，公務員有需要了解內地社會發展和經濟情況、政治體制、政府架構及運作，以掌握最新資料，配合國家的發展，絕不認同議員提出要取消公務員參加國情班的安排。<br />\n<br />\n羅智光強調，公務員堅守法治，保持政治中立，執法人員亦一貫嚴格按照《基本法》、相關法例，不偏不倚履行職務。"},{"pid":"4adab3a07b0955073d2d136f6cb158872b9118f0","tid":1187019,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:37:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1116454&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1116454%26csid%3D261_341&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElqEelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=240509f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1116454&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"f5f78d122a6c9620761b7d4ee185906f7367f92d","tid":1187019,"uid":389,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"距離跟大陸人工不遠"},{"pid":"a7a665eb54e865f937803176f1cefd780211d3e1","tid":1187019,"uid":173598,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:03:42.000Z","msg":"距離請大陸人做公務員不遠"},{"pid":"04c3393860b41a1dc5f4cdecb56603dfb05c6a8a","tid":1187019,"uid":3929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:05:53.000Z","msg":"諗起有班公務